Name: Canned Mollusc
Description: Freshly harvested mollusc's from a crab pot or foraged now in can form.

DescriptionLocalization.es: Moluscos recién recolectados de una cesta de cangrejos, ahora en forma de lata.
DescriptionLocalization.ko: 통발에서 수확한 신선한 연체통물으로 만든 통조림.
DescriptionLocalization.fr: Mollusque fraîchement récolté d'un casier à crabes ou de la cueillette, dorénavant en boîte.
DescriptionLocalization.zh: 可以从觅食或者蟹笼中收获新鲜的软体动物，把它们加工成罐头。
